            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1611577912994-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced mushrooms</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until starting to brown</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>thyme</strong> and cook for 2 min further</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1611683890300-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
