    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, pour <strong>1/4</strong> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1/8]</span> of the <strong>batter</strong> (approximately 100ml) into the pan</p><p>Lift the pan and tilt it in a circular motion so that the mixture spreads evenly across the whole of the base</p><p>Once evenly spread, cook for 2 min or until the pancake is set</p><p>Once set, use a spatula to carefully flip the pancake over</p>",
